Survey.FlockScript: function shuffle(array) { 		var counter = array.length, temp, index; 	    while (counter > 0) { 	      index = Math.floor(Math.random() * counter); 	      counter--; 	      temp = array[counter]; 	      array[counter] = array[index]; 	      array[index] = temp; 	  } 	  return array; 	}	 	var c = fSUR.getChapters()[0]; 	var q = c.getQuestions()[0]; 	q.setQuestionText("Random number: " + Math.floor(Math.random() * (10 - 2 + 1)) + 2); 	var answers = shuffle(q.getAnswers()); 	q.setAnswers(answers); 	c.setQuestions(new Array(q)); 	fSUR.setChapters(new Array(c));
